node.text:
Did you know that we have washable rugs? 🤩 Now you don't have to worry about the spills, you can live in the moment!! 🤗✌🏼 Check out our washable rugs so you can enjoy family time and stop worrying on how to clean the rug. Just throw it in the washing machine and let the magic begin! ✨ 

We had a fun time shooting this with our team - hope you had fun watching it! Thanks James and Robert 😂😊 #boutiquerugs #washable

node.title: Enjoy life with BoutiqueRugs washable rugs!

node.text:
Do you want to add carpet to your stairs? To have it done professionally can be costly, but @revealmydiy has a solution for you! Grab one of our runners (which are great for DIY projects!) and follow the instructions in this video! Soon, your stairs will be both stylish and plush! 
.
